       500-GMNHEN-SEC              SECTION.
      *
           INITIALIZE                  M02
      *      *
           IF      SYS-1010-GSRAUTH(1:1)    =  "0"
               CONTINUE
           ELSE
               MOVE    SPA-GMN-GSEL        TO  M02-SELNUM
           END-IF
